Twitter user Arke USA from Bryant, Arkansas, filmed the ice balls peppering his backyard and noisily plopping into the pool .
Footage shows the hailstones coming down at speed, with many cracking as they hit the ground .
The National Weather Service received 170 reports of hail on Tuesday, twenty of which detailed stones at least two inches in diameter .
There have been reports of power outages and traffic delays due to the severe weather .